
This app is up and running in following web address:
http://hollow-dusk-1801.herokuapp.com/

Source code is avialable in following web address:
https://github.com/smoradi/flogger

or use one of these commands directly to get source code.

$ git clone git://github.com/smoradi/flogger.git flogger
$ git clone https://github.com/smoradi/flogger.git flogger

To run this application locally run following commands in root of project

$ mvn package           # My Maven version was 3.0.4
$ export PORT=1199      # 1199 could be any number higher than 1000,
$ java -cp target/classes:"target/dependency/*" HelloWorld

Now enter http://localhost:1199 into address bar of your web browser.

Currently there are two ways of accessing content of this blog.

http://HOST/app/file?name=FILE_NAME
http://HOST/data/FILE_NAME

For example:
http://localhost:1199/app/file?name=startMyBlog.xml
http://localhost:1199/data/startMyBlog.xml

http://hollow-dusk-1801.herokuapp.com/app/file?name=startMyBlog.xml
http://hollow-dusk-1801.herokuapp.com/data/startMyBlog.xml

